snippet.title: Poobette
snippet.description:
I explore the world unconventionally, and seek unexpected absurdity. Come along for the mild amusement and occasional naughty pun.

We take digital road trips and explore small town America, visiting either weird towns or towns with funny names - but the name is just a gateway to interesting local history, life, and even the best of Google Maps, Google Reviews, and property for sale. We follow up with input from locals too, so please share your stories in the comments.

Otherwise, we often explore weird news, funny crimes and other local happenings around the world, and sometimes a little gameplay.
